        "meta_description": "The cynical Basil Fawlty is set to return in a modern day revival of the iconic sitcom Fawlty Towers - but news of the return was a 'surprise' to the original series' co-writer",
        "meta_lang": "en",
        "meta_favicon": "https://s2-prod.devonlive.com/@trinitymirrordigital/chameleon-branding/publications/devonlive/img/favicon.addf3ad78d52f6ad.ico",
        "meta_site_name": "Devon Live",
